1a:T433,External evidence reveals BioMime is actually a PRODUCT FAMILY with multiple distinct variants (BioMime, BioMime Aura, BioMime Lineage), not a single product. All variants share: Meril manufacturer, Sirolimus-eluting, Cobalt-Chromium platform, ultra-thin 65μm struts. However, internal catalog treats this as single product without variant differentiation. External sources confirm basic specifications (Sirolimus DES, CoCr platform, extensive clinical data) but reveal product line complexity not captured in current catalog structure. Conflict: catalog presents unified product where manufacturer markets distinct variants with different delivery systems and design features (Novel Hybrid Design vs Monolithic Design). Recommended action is review to determine if: (1) catalog should remain family-level entry, (2) should split into variant-specific pages, or (3) vendor supplies single consolidated SKU despite multiple commercial variants. Current title lacks drug specification clarity for clinical users. Material and drug classifications confirmed across all sources.16:["$","$L19",null,{"product":{"product_name":"BioMime Drug Eluting Stent","product_name_display":"BioMime Drug Eluting Stent","sku_code":"MRL-CARD-004","product_family":"BioMime Drug Eluting Stent","product_family_display":"BioMime Drug Eluting Stent","slug":"biomime-drug-eluting-stent","images":[{"id":"fa5200c096c3","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c17bd504841ec9248cfaca/cover_bbe0584f.jpg","original_filename":"cover_biomime Brochure.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":1782294,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:58:48.902319+00:00","source":"brochure_extraction","width":4961,"height":2339},{"id":"f913022cb8f5","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c17bd504841ec9248cfaca/cover_8be576cc.jpg","original_filename":"cover_biomime Brochure.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":1782294,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T06:02:58.617854+00:00","source":"brochure_extraction","width":4961,"height":2339}],"st